---
title: Easy Sticky Beef & Asparagus Stir-Fry with Corn Rice & Coriander
description: This Asian-style beef and asparagus stir fry is calling our name and we can’t resist! Our blend of spices and sauces creates the perfect balance of sweet and savoury and even the corn-studded rice is bursting with flavour. You’ll be back for seconds and thirds of this one.
